    base:desc "The overall architecture links the physical crane to a Python interface, which communicates via MQTT to DT services (trajectory generation, simulation, continuous validation). Data is persisted in a TimescaleDB database and visualized on a Grafana dashboard; operators interact through a Python HMI front‑end."
